# MILESTONES

## 0.1.x
* Controller Support
* config file saving

## 0.1.2
* MIDI support (by way of MidiAudioImporter Magnum-Plugin)

## 0.1.1
* Resolution settings
* Screen Settings
** Pixel Perfect (multiple of base resolution (320*224))
** Zoom
** Stretch

## 0.1.0
* ReadMe
* Build Instructions

## 0.0.8
* OpenFF-libs integration
** ff7 field level image loading

## 0.0.7
* Music:
** multiple songs
** song skipping
* Async, non-blocking file-loading

## 0.0.6
* Multiple Types of Textboxes
** (Default) Textbox (w/ default text offset)
** Freeform Textbox (multiple, individual, monospaced Chars (w/ Char-Matrix);
                     definable offset (global and per-char))
** Menu Textbox (w/ indented text offset)
* Input-Callback on Textboxes
** Keyboard-Type Input
** Controller-Type Input
** Mouse-Type Input

## 0.0.5
* UI
** Font by: http://caveras.net/

## 0.0.4
* Audio Playback
* configurable keybinds for
** increasing/decreasing gain
** pausing/resuming

## 0.0.3
* Configuration file loading
* ff7-data path configuration
* basic input handling
* config load error handling

## 0.0.2
* Background Rendering

## 0.0.1
* General Source Layout
